Keep Garfield satiated (full) or he will eat anything you are carrying and
make the game unfinishable.

To open the CATFLAP:  Get the spade from the shed and drop it next to the
catflap.  Watch what happens!  Weird puzzles abound in this game.

WALKTHROUGH
Take the lamp from the bedroom.
Find and eat the aniseed.
Go to garden shed and fall through hole and keep going right.
Go down, and down again and then go right to find NERMAL.
Kick him till he drops the mouse.
Let Odie pick up the mouse.
Drop the lamp and take the mouse from Odie.
Go to the health shop and drop the mouse.
Pick up the spinach donut.
Go to the pizza party and go left to the big rat.
Drop the donut and boot the chest when it runs away.
Take the key from the chest.
Go up and back to the park.
Drop the key near the bench and go back to the garden.
Take the bucket or spade and go to the hardware shop.
Use the object and take the dollar.
Get the bird seed.
Go back to the bench and drop the seed and take the key.
When the bird comes, hitch a ride to the pound.
Now follow the doors.

End.
